en: Deliver parcel to the train station post office.
Host the event in one of your White Ash Harbor restaurants.
Host the event in one of your Billboard City restaurants.
(npc) is hosting a party and requires ingredients to make a special snack.
(npc) wants to cook a dish for a friend and (pronoun_D) wants you to find a special ingredient.
(npc) wants to try out a new dish and requires some ingredients.
(npc) is making a present for a friend and needs a rare item to finish (pronoun_P) project.
Collect a rare item to add to (npc)'s collection.
(npc) wants to make a gift for a friend in Billboard City and (pronoun_D) needs a special item to create it.
(npc) is craving your restaurant's (dishname). Prepare a takeout order for (npc).
(npc) wants to spend the day relaxing, but (pronoun_D) cannot do it without your famous (dishname).
(npc) wants to spend a day at the beach, and hopes to have your famous (dishname) to accompany (pronoun_P).
(npc) is hosting a small party and would really love an order of your (dishname).
(npc) is going up for a hike in the mountains and would like an order of your famous (dishname).
(npc) wants to send a care package to (pronoun_P) family in Billboard City.
Help deliver (npc)'s parcel of clothes for the children's shelter. What a good samaritan!
(npc) needs help returning (pronoun_P) Omozone order, which was damaged during shipping.
(npc) has made a gift-wrapped present for (pronoun_P) idol in Billboard City.
Help deliver (npc)'s wrapped gift to a penpal in Billboard City. Who could it be?
(animal)s are swarming the beaches of White Ash Harbor. Reduce their population and keep them away from beachgoers.
(animal)s have been venturing past the beach boundary and have snuck into peoples' homes. Drive back the (animal) invasion.
(animal)s have been ravaging the countryside and are damaging the local farms. Hunt (animal)s to protect the crops.
Recently, tourists have been attacked and injured by enraged (animal)s. Reduce their population to prevent further attacks.
(animal)s have been ambushing people in the deep woods without warning. Defeat (animal)s to prevent more attacks.
(npc) wants to make a bet with an experienced hunter. Defeat (animal)s within the time limit to win a prize.
(animal)s are destroying the crops in Takashi Farms. Reduce their population to protect the crops.
(npc) wants to make a bet with an experienced hunter. Hunt (animal)s within the time limit to win a prize.
(npc) wants to host a fun little party for (pronoun_P) friends in White Ash Harbor.
(npc) is hosting a fan party for a famous musician, and wants a cozy setting with good food and drinks.
It's the weekend, which means it's the perfect time for a big BBQ to celebrate. (npc) needs a lively setting with a great meat menu.
(npc) wants to host a meetup to chat about all things technology and gaming. Provide a suitable setting for (pronoun_P) guests to enjoy themselves.
It's (npc)'s birthday. (pronoun_P) would love to party the day away and drink away (pronoun_P) sorrows and regrets.
It's (npc)'s turn to host a gathering for the Polite Society. (npc) politely requests an elegant setting with some comfort foods.
(npc) is hungry and wants to have a big feast for (pronoun_F) and (pronoun_P) family. Create a grand feast for (npc).
(npc) loves sweets wants to invite (pronoun_P) friends for a cozy tea party.
(npc) wants to host a seafood feast for (pronoun_P) fellow fishermen. Create a lively feast centered around seafood.
(npc) would like to have a party for (pronoun_P) vegan friends. Ideally, this party would be hosted in a room with a modern decor.
The Frozen Fanatics are an elite culinary group that travel around the globe to eat frozen foods. (npc) is a member and it's (pronoun_P) turn to host their next gathering.
(npc) has been feeling down lately and would to to enjoy a private meal at one of your restaurants.
(npc) would like to host a cocktail party for (pronoun_P) fellow amateur alcohol connoisseurs. Provide a nice drink menu and a hip setting.
Return to (npc) to claim your reward.
Meet the locals and learn about gathering ingredients. Open Le Sequoia for the first time and prepare a meal for Hasel.
Speak to Uriel the butcher about acquiring meats.
Speak to farmer May Lou about gathering vegetables.
Speak to fruit seller Nabiha to learn about fruits.
Speak to fisherman Aloys to learn about fishing.
Speak to Thelio to learn about baking supplies.
Return to Hasel at Le Sequoia Restaurant.
Set up the restaurant by meeting the requirements and prepare a meal for Hasel.
You have completed your first service. Speak to hasel outside.
The refrigerator of Le Sequoia is old and small. Have Bianca help you upgrade the refrigerator with a new one.
Speak to Bianca to fix the refrigerator.
Bianca can help you but she needs you to retrieve an item from Thelio.
Delivery the box of sweets back to Bianca and she will help you with the fridge.
Bianca is heading over to Le Sequoia to fix the refrigerator. Meet her there.
Host a soft opening of Le Sequoia for a small group of White Ash harbor residents.
Hasel will gather up some locals to attend the soft opening. Prepare the restaurant for the soft opening and wait until the next day to speak to her.
When you are ready, speak to Hasel to prepare for the Le Sequoia's soft opening.
Open Le Sequoia when you are ready to host the soft opening, with a menu featuring at least 3 dishes and seating for 4 guests.
The soft opening of Le Sequoia is complete. Speak to the guests outside.
The restaurant interior needs to be cleaned up before you can have a grand opening.
Speak to Prisca at the Town Hall to have the floors fixed.
Prisca left her tools in the abandoned bathhouse.
Go into the abandoned bathhouse and retrieve the carpenter's tools.
Search the abandoned bathhouse to find the carpenter's tools.
Return the carpentry tools to Prisca.
Select a new floor type for Le Sequoia from Prisca.
Prisca will have the floors fixed after one day.
The floors should now be fixed. Meet Prisca back at Le Sequoia.
Prepare the grand opening of Le Sequoia. Prepare a suitable menu and decor to make a good first impression.
Hasel might have some ideas on preparing for the grand opening.
Milo is an experienced designer. He will have ideas on decorating Le Sequoia.
Aloys might have some rope needed for the decorations. Find him by the docks.
Search the nearby buckets for some rope.
Collect (10 x Clam Shells) and (30 x Watercress). Bring these items back to Milo, along with the rope.
Wait a day for Milo to complete the decorations.
Return to Milo and see if the decorations are complete.
Wait for Milo to complete the decorations.
When you are ready, let Hasel know that you want to begin the grand opening. You will not be able to host a regular restaurant service until the grand opening is over.
Prepare Le Sequoia with a menu featuring at least 6 dishes and seating for 8 guests. Open the restaurant between 2.P.M and 6 P.M. to begin the grand opening.
The grand opening of Le Sequoia is complete. Speak to the Hasel outside.
April needs some help with her tea research.
Speak to April near the Lonely Cliffs.
Collect 30 Chili, 30 Elderberries, and 30 Sugar Cane for April.
Use the Tea Dispneser to mix a new tea for April.
Help Thelio recover the missing store goods.
Search the beach caves for signs of the thieves.
The old house inside the caves looks suspicious. Maybe I should take a closer look?
You have found some leftover scraps from the stolen goods. Show this to Thelio.
Speak to Bianca about crafting a Flour Mill.
Bianca requires some materials for crafting a Flour Mill. Bring her 10 Iron ore, 15 Plant Roots, 5 Copper Ore, and 5 bottles of Mead. You can purchase Drills from Bianca to mine ore.
Delivery 30 pieces of Sorghum to Thelio. Some wild Sorghum can be found near the cliffs beside the bathhouse.
Meet Thelio and Bianca at Bianca's shop.
Anna-May will help you make some decorations.
Anna-May might be able to help you with decorations. Find her at Takashi farms.
Anna-May has decided to make some new lamps for Le Sequoia. Bring Anna-May 5 pieces of Uncut Quartz.
Anna-May requires some inspiration to continue her work. Provide a restaurant service for her so she can understand the essence of Le Sequoia, with a menu featuring at least 4 dishes.
Speak to Anna-May outside Le Sequoia.
Anna-May has begun working on the new furniture pieces. Wait one day before visiting her.
Visit Anna-May inside the Takashi farmhouse.
Lucius Delacourt will eat at Le Sequoia and deliver a critic review.
Prepare Le Sequoia with a menu featuring at least 7 dishes and seating for 8 guests. Open Le Sequoia between 10 A.M. and 6 P.M. when you are ready for Lucius Delacourt's arrival.
Wait one day for Lucius' review of Le Sequoia.
Read Lucius' review of Le Sequoia.
Lucius has not left White Ash Harbor and instead has a mysterious request.
Meet Lucius in room 201 of Hotel Rose.
Something is stirring in the abandoned Peony Bathhouse.
Chef Casteau is back, and asks you for a favor. Meet him at the Peony Bathhouse between 8 PM and midnight.
Speak to Bianca about make some copper pipes to help repair the bathhouse.
Bring Bianca 5 Copper Ores and 5 Iron Ores for the pipes, and 5 bottles of Vodka as payment.
Wait one day for Bianca to finish crafting the copper pipes.
Visit Bianca at her shop to pick up the copper pipes.
Bring the completed copper pipes back to Nadjet at the abandoned bathhouse.
Learn the Peony Bathhouse's secret method of creating a great bathing experience.
Purchase some Instant Ice Packs from Valentina at the infirmary.
Head into the volcano and mine 15 pieces of Sulpur to bring back to Nadjet.
Successfully mix a Bath Blok in the bathhouse mechanical room.
Gain Aylin's trust and host a soft opening at the Teahouse.
In order to gain Aylin's trust, you must complete a restaurant service at Le Sequoia and end the service with a total Reputation of 300.
You have gained the required reputation at Le Sequoia. Speak to Aylin at the Bathhouse.
Aylin has given you the keys to the Teahouse. Visit your new restaurant.
Host a soft opening at the Teahouse between 10 A.M. and 6 P.M., with a menu featuring at least 6 dishes and seating for 10 guests.
You have completed the Teahouse soft opening. Speak to the Bathhouse staff in the lobby.
Nadjet is facing a sudden problem that could jeopardize the bathhouse's grand opening.
Prepare Le Sequoia and host Nadjet's dinner between 5 P.M. and 9 P.M., with a menu featuring at least 6 dishes and seating for 4 guests.
Nadjet's dinner for Damien has concluded. Speak to them outside.
Make the final preparations for the grand opening of the Peony Bathhouse.
Fill up all 3 Bathhouse baths with Bath Bloks.
Let Aylin know when you are ready to begin the grand opening.
Open the Teahouse between 10 A.M. and 6 P.M. to begin the grand opening, with a menu featuring at least 10 dishes and seating for 20 guests.
The grand opening is over. Speak to Aylin in her office.
Help Pomarine defeat the Ancient Razorback.
Prepare your supplies for the final hunt and wait for one day. Return to Pomarine when you are ready.
When you have prepared your hunting supplies, let Pomarine know that you are ready.
Create a new Gazing Ball for April after a boar destroyed her home.
You should ask Bianca about the method for extracting perfect quartz.
Now that you have a method of extracting perfect quartz crystals, look for a large quartz growth in the White Ash Harbor caves.
Now that you extracted a perfect quartz, Speak to April again regarding creating a new crystal ball.
Anna-May is a local sculpture. She may be able to help shape the quartz crystal.
Anna-May isn't feeling very well. She requires some headache medicine before she can continue to work.
Meet Anna-May at Takashi Farmhouse to retrieve the polished crystal.
Cook offerings of 3 Vegitable Dishes as a gesture of goodwill to the spirits of the forest, so that they will bless the crystal ball. (0/3 Cooked)
Cook offerings of 3 Vegitable Dishes as a gesture of goodwill to the spirits of the forest, so that they will bless the crystal ball. (1/3 Cooked)
Cook offerings of 3 Vegitable Dishes as a gesture of goodwill to the spirits of the forest, so that they will bless the crystal ball. (2/3 Cooked)
Now that you have prepared 3 dishes to offer to the forest spirits, you must bring the crystal ball and offerings to the altar in the deep forest.
The crystal ball and food offerings have been placed on the altar. Leave the crystal ball on the altar overnight to attract the spirits.
You have left the crystal ball in the woods overnight. You should check to see if the offering worked.
The gazing ball emanates a new and strange energy. Bring the gazing ball back to April.
Do not receive buffs from most consumable items.
Chance of higher-rarity chefs for hire.
Chance of higher-rarity waiters for hire.
Uriel can often be found at his butcher shop Chop, in the town center.
Aloys is a fisherman and can often be found around the White Ash Harbor docks.
Hasel can often be found at her shop Bubble Shack, on the western side of town.
Aime can often be found training in White Ash Harbor's rec center by the docks.
Bianca can often be found in her electronics shop Bits & Pieces, by the waterfront promenade.
Pomarine's house is found along the western coast, where she regularly goes hunting.
April runs a gift shop from her home, west of Le Sequoia.
Nacim works at Circuit Lodge and can often be found at the hotel reception.
Anna-May can often be found around Takashi farms.
Mae-Lou can often be found at her vegi shop in the town center, or working the fields in her farm.
Prisca is the assistant to the mayor, and works at the Town Hall.
Bowie can often be found at his seafood stall at the docks, or wandering the western cliffs.
Milo can often be found at his clothing shop in White Ash Harbor's waterfront promenade.
Valentina can often be found working in White Ash Harbor's infirmary.
Bea can often be found at her bar at night, in the town center.
Aylin runs the Bathhouse and can often be found in her office.
Nadjet can often be found working at the Bathhouse.
Thelio can often be found working at Milk & Wheat in the town center.
Lucius is currently staying at a room in Hotel Rose. He usually takes strolls around the promenade area.
Nabiha can often be found at her fresh fruit shop in the town center.
T.E.C. can be found to his Takoyaki diner at the docks.
Elton can be found working at the convenience store 8-11.
Robert is the head bellhop in Hotel Rose, and can be found in the lobby.
Yvonne is a bellhop can often be found working in Hotel Rose.
Cora can often be found working at White Ash Harbor docks.
Leon is the ship captain and can often be found at White Ash Harbor docks.
Mary Anne can often be found wandering around Takashi farms.
Casper can often be found wandering around Takashi farms.
Gavin is the Mayor of White Ash Harbor and can be found at the Town Hall.
Mei can often be found working at the Bathhouse.
Farhan can often be found working at the Bathhouse.
Duncan can often be found working at the Bathhouse.
Dimitri is a Lelsh empolyee who works at the train station ticket office.
Alisa is a Lelsh empolyee who works at the train station ticket office.
Benjamin can often be found working at Parcel Co. by the train station.
Ema is a barista who works on the high-speed train.
Sahil is a Lelsh employee who works at the Lelsh office in White Ash Harbor.
Duri is a Lelsh employee who works at the Lelsh office in White Ash Harbor.
Henri can often be found in his furniture shop La Galerie, in White Ash Harbor.
Asher can be found working as the conductor in the high-speed train.
Eliza can often be found working at the Library, in White Ash Harbor.
Alice works as Lucius' assistant and can usually be found at his office.
Uriel is a friendly butcher who always seems to be working. He wishes for the success of Le Sequoia, and hopes he can provide quality meats for your dishes.
Aloys is a fisherman of few words. Despite his cool and mysterious demeanor, he has always been helpful, and talks to strangers like friends.
An older generation android, Hasel was abandoned in a dumpster within Billboard City, before being recovered by Aloys. A small frog was found with her, and has never left her side since.
A competitive body builder who loves to show off his gains. Just like his wife Bea, he loves to live life to the fullest and won't ever decline an invitation to a party.
A gifted programmer and mechanic, Bianca is a cold woman with questionable morality. She can be extremely helpful through her skills, for the right price of course.
As one of the oldest residents of White Ash Harbor, Pomarine's looks can be deceiving. She is a fierce hunter who loves to experience life in the wilderness, and a mentor for all aspiring rangers.
April is a strange woman who seemingly possesses clairvoyant powers. She was recently travelling through exotic lands to grow her research towards herbs and teas.
Nacim manages the Circuit Lodge in White Ash Harbor and dedicates his time towards his daughters. He always puts on a friendly face and hopes for Le Sequoia to succeed.
Anna-May is a shy girl who rarely comes out of her home in Takashi Farms. Polar opposites from her sister Mae-Lou, she prefers to spend her time on her scultures and playing video games.
Mae-Lou is a friendly farmer who lives in Takashi Farms with her parents and her twin sister Anna-May. She seems content with her rustic life, and takes pleasure in being in the fields.
Prisca is a tenacious woman who is always working hard to improve the state White Ash Harbor. She forgoes personal pleasure and pursues her work, often to an unhealthy degree.
On the surface, Bowie seems like a relaxed old man who wants to do as little as possible each day. He spends his days running his seafood store, and taking strolls along the seaside cliffs.
Angi is a young android man living a spoiled life with his wealthy adopted human mother. He is unsure of his purpose in life, greater amplified by being him being a non-human.
Fleur runs a famous cafe in Billboard City, passed down to her by her family. She is still coming to terms with her new responsibilities, and still wishes to live a spontaneous lifestyle.
Milo sells clothing by the lower promenade in White Ash Harbor. He has a quirky personality and can be impolite at times. He seems like he has a crush on Hasel.
Valentina manages the infirmary in White Ash Harbor, despite not having a medical degree. Still, the locals go to her for medical aid. She has a reserved personality, and mostly keeps to herself.
When not managing her 6 kids, Bea manages the local bar in White Ash Harbor's town square, creating delicious cocktails that the tourists can't get enough of.
Aylin is an android woman who is always dressed in her signature blue Kimono. She is mysterious and quiet, but has an air of confidence and power surrounding her. She owns the bathhouse.
Nadjet is Aylin's passionate and diligent helper. She runs the day-to-day in the Peony Bathhouse, and does everything she can to make sure Aylin is happy.
Thelio helps run the Milk & Wheat shop for his boss. Despite being rather cold to strangers, he warms up to people after sharing experiences and accomplishing tasks together.
Lucius is a famous food critic from Billboard City. His reviews have closed down restaurants of top chefs. He desires your support after seeing your talent, but has not revealed his true goals.
Nabiha is a lively, upbeat woman who sells fruits. She is a free spirit, and has travelled and experienced the world. She now practices veganism, and hopes you do the same for the restaurant.
Damien is one of the heads of the Columbo crime family, based in Billboard City. In the past, he was the original guardian of Nadjet and sent her to steal the deed to the Peony Bathhouse.

Hugo is an officer of the LELSH Corporation. He has been tasked with a mysterious mission involving the volcano of White Ash Harbor. You can often find him poking around the volcano base and collecting samples.
Koa is an old friend and chef who studied under Vincent Casteau. He dreams of one day running his own successful restaurant. His competitiveness has always pushed you forward.
Camille is an old friend and chef who studied under Vincent Casteau. She dreams of one day running her own successful restaurant. Her competitiveness has always pushed you forward.
Vincent Casteau is a renowned chef and a mentor that taught you cooking. After leaving his first restaurant Le Sequoia, he went on to run several successful restaurants around the country.
Otto Canton was your former boss, who has a propensity towards outbursts of anger, especially towards his staff. Despite his obnoxious personality, he is an extremely skilled chef.
Uriel is a passionate butcher who is often overworked. Despite his friendly and boisterous demeanor, he prefers quiet activities with close friends, and enjoying a cup of hot tea.
Aloys is a fisherman who dreams of a different life. In fact, he has always loved machines and is saving money to go to engineering school. He also enjoys collecting vintage clothes.
Hasel is an android girl who is always accompanied by her frog Boba. Despite being an older android model who suffers from frequent bugs, she always possesses a positive outlook.
Aime is a boisterous man who is a loving father to his 6 kids, and loving husband to his wife Bea. He works as a fitness trainer in the local recreation center, helping others grow their muscles.
Bianca is an engineering genius who has grown to love the quiet life of White Ash Harbor. Despite her cold demeanor, she deeply cares for the locals and is a loyal friend to those she trusts.
The legendary hunter of White Ash Harbor, Pomarine has slowed down her adventuring lifestyle due to her older age. Despite a weaker body, she still possess a fiery temperament.
Despite engaging with the spiritual arts, April possesses deep practical knowledge of various herbs and teas. She is friendly and helpful through her own peculiar ways.
A widow and a father of two girls, Nacim dedicates his time to creating crafts and exploring the beautiful outdoors with his kids. He is also an avid gamer in his free time.
Anna-May is a talented sculptor that prefers to spend her time indoors. Despite being polar-opposites with her twin sister, they have always loved and supported each other.
Mae-Lou is a hardworking farmer who spends her time working the fields and running her veggie shop. She also takes care of her aging parents, and helping out her twin sister when she can.
Prisca is the aide to White Ash Harbor's mayor. She cares deeply for the wellbeing of the town, and is often frantically running around town completing her tasks.
Bowie is Uriel's grandfather and the local fishmonger. He has adventured across the whole world, and has decided to settle for a quiet life in White Ash Harbor in his old age.
Angi is a spoiled android boy who is seeking his own path in life. His life in Billboard City has been comfy and cushy, so emerging out of his bubble has been a difficult journey.
A spontaneous girl living in Billboard City, Fleur has a complicated relationship with her demanding family. Fleur has been given the task of running her successful family owned caf.
A quirky man who sells clothes in White Ash Harbor. He is deeply passionate about his clothing designs, and also makes Oni Masks as a hobby.
Although not a licensed doctor, Valentina has the difficult task of managing the local clinic. To alleviate stress from her high-demand job, she indulges in horror films and watches combat sports.
Bea is a vibrant woman who is a loving mother to her 6 kids, and a loving wife to her husband Aime. She runs her bar every night, and loves going to the beach or taking a hot bath.
An android woman with a complex past. Aylin was once human and is one of the few humans to undergo android transformation to save her life. She now manages the Peony Bathhouse.
Nadjet dedicates her life in support of Aylin and the bathhouse. She was once a member of a criminal organisation, before escaping and coming to White Ash Harbor to begin a new life.
Thelio is a young man struggling with his sense of purpose. He currently helps manage the Milk & Wheat shop but hopes to do something significant one day. He enjoys reading.
A well-known food critic in the culinary world, Lucius puts on a kind facade but hides a rotten personality underneath. Despite his personality, he cares deeply for the culinary arts.
Once a reality show contestant in her youth, Nabiha experienced a lavish lifestyle full of parties and designer clothes. She decided to move to White Ash Harbor to become closer with nature
Koa is a talented chef who like yourself, grew up under the tutelage chef Vincent Casteau. He runs his own restaurant in Billboard City, and hopes to push the limits of delicious food.
Camille is a talented chef who like yourself, grew up under the tutelage chef Vincent Casteau. She runs her own restaurant in Billboard City, and hopes to push the limits of delicious food.
Vincent Casteau is world-renowned chef and the former owner of Le Sequoia. He has taught many young chefs throughout his career, and is known for helping communities through food.
Otto Canton is a harsh chef who runs one of the top restaurants in Billboard City. At one point your former boss, he continues to terrorize young chefs in his pursuit of culinary perfection.
Overwrite your autosave file with previous sleep save file from (time)?
Overwrite your autosave file with previous story quest (quest) complete save file?
Are you sure you want to delete this character?
This game has autosave. Separate save files are made when your player goes to sleep, and after completing a main story quest.
Loading one of these save files will overwrite the autosave save file.
OMG I was here in the library on a Tuesday night and I saw Eliza the librarian with a strange man. It was dark, but I think they were kissing!! Ewwww.
I think that man was wearing a green sweater, and had a weird round hat. I feel like I've seen him somewhere before . . .
Prisca was being a BIG MEANIE today. I asked her if she wanted to kick a football with me, and she told me to help her collect trash!
I don't even like garbage! Now I have to sit in this lame library all day until my dad picks me up.
I want to throw a big party and invite all my friends from school! I want to buy lots of alcohol since I heard from Fred that it makes parties more fun.
My mom says I can't drink alcohol until I am 18. I guess the party will have to wait until my 18th birthday. Only 10 more years to go!
Guess what! I heard that I am getting an FunStation 420 for my birthday. I already know what games I will be getting. This is going to be the best birthday ever!
You gotta come over so we can play together. It's no fun to play with my brothers. They never take games seriously.
Ok. I have hidden the package under the librarian's desk. She doesen't have a clue, ha! Be sure that nobody is looking when you go pick it up.
My dad would kill me if he found out I had these. And make sure you keep it away from your parents too! If we get caught, you will be sorry!
I was in math class this morning and Tom kept staring at me. I think he likes me. It's kinda gross. You know that I like Kevin. He is so cool, especially when he is on his skateboard.
But Kevin always seems to hang around Avril. I don't get what her deal is? What does Kevin see in her? She always wears her ugly black outfits. I said hi to her last week and she totally ignored me!

Hey dude, I really messed up today. I was kicking my ball in the library today and it accidently hit Olga in the face. Next thing I knew, she was on the floor crying and Mrs. Eliza was screaming at me!
I hate school. Why do we have to sit in this building all day? I just want to go out and throw rocks over the Lonely Cliffs. I bet I can throw farther than you can!
Ok hear me out. I just had an amazing idea! I was thinking we can start a secret boxing club up by the Lonely cliffs. The adults won't be able to find us there!
Your dad owns the dojo right? I was thinking you can grab a couple gloves from the dojo. We will only invite kids we trust. I will be the president of the club, and you can be the helper!
Mom doesen't want me to play Brutal Fighter Online anymore. She even took away my GameDot Console and almost grounded me! This sucks.
I wish my parents were like yours. I can't believe you get to play Brutal Fighter any time you want.
I saw something VERY SCARY today. I was walking past the bathhouse when I saw a ghost by the entrance! It was very dark, and it entered the bathhouse even without any lights on.

It's body was waving, almost like it was floating. It must be a ghost! Who would walk into a dark empty building like that? I got so scared I immediately ran back into the Library. Eliza wouldn't believe me!
Become a pitmaster and discover new talents when cooking with a variety of meats. You can also improve you proficiency when cooking with Grills and Ovens.
Master the art of vegetarian cuisine. Unlock brand new vegetarian recipes, improve your cooking speed, and improve the happiness of your guests with health-conscious cooking.
Become a master of dough, and enhance the quality of your baked goods. Learn the art of ingredient management to save ingredients when cooking.
Learn the art of drink mixing, and bring a new culinary dimension to the beverages you serve. Learn faster drink mixing, and improve the satisfaction of customers who try your drinks.
Master the art of seafood cuinsine, and enhance your menu with the flavors of the ocean. You can also improve you proficiency when cooking with Steamers and Friers.
Learn the art of molecular gastronomy and use science to produce otherworldy cuisine. You can also improve you proficiency when cooking with Stoves and Ice Cream Makers.

Dropped ingredients will be returned to inventory.
View brewing recipes that you have previously discovered.

Extract the juice without the skin.

(name) has visited your restaurant. Check your mail on the following day to see the review.
(name) visited your restaurant but there was not enough food to serve. The critic will return.
Learn -Supply Chain- skill to unlock ingredient deliveries.
You've got this! Running a restaurant is hard but remember that I'm always here for you.
Your restaurant is going to be amazing! Hope this can help in some way.
Hey bud. Came across this the other day and thought it might help!
Sending you my best wishes and looking forward to the great success to your restaurant!
Always fun chatting with you friend. I found this the other day and thought of you.
Hey (playername), looking forward to seeing you more around town. It's always been a pleasure.
I am happy to have met you and getting to know you more and more. And than you for always listening. Let's hang out soon!
I just wanted to say how impressive the growth of Le Sequoia has been. It has had a great postive impact on White Ash Harbor. Wishing you more success!
Hi (playername), you've been a great help to me and the rest of the folks here. Feel free to drop by my home anytime if you want to chat.
